# Spring Initializr рџљЂ

## рџ“– What is Spring Initializr?

**Spring Initializr** is a web-based tool that helps developers quickly create and configure Spring Boot projects.

It automatically generates a ready-to-use project structure with the required dependencies and build files.

Instead of manually creating folders and configuration files, Spring Initializr generates everything for you.

---

# рџЋЇ Why Use Spring Initializr?

Without Spring Initializr:

вќЊ Create project structure manually

вќЊ Configure Maven/Gradle manually

вќЊ Add dependencies one by one

вќЊ Setup Spring Boot configuration

With Spring Initializr:

вњ… Generate project instantly

вњ… Add dependencies automatically

вњ… Ready-to-run project

вњ… Saves development time

